name: Portraits from the Multiverse - Diverse Friends - Monica
description:
Portraits from the Multiverse is a series of AI-generated works that imagine alternate realities where things are not quite what they are now. Diverse Friends explores what the cast of a popular sitcom would look like with more ethnic and cultural diversity in the lead roles.

You can read about how I created the series here, https://robgon.medium.com/list/portraits-from-the-multiverse-583b06d2130e
